            "title": "ANNUAL SURVIVAL AND POPULATION ESTIMATES OF MOUNTAIN PLOVERS IN SOUTHERN PHILLIPS COUNTY, MONTANA",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Stephen J.",
