            "title": "Persist or Perish: Can Bats Threatened with Extinction Persist and Recover from White-nose Syndrome?",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Tina L",
                    "lastName": "Cheng"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
