            "title": "Quantifying rosy-finch migration with stable hydrogen isotope feather markers highlights the need for inter-state collaboration to reach conservation goals",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Caitlin",
                    "lastName": "Campbell"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
